release_note: Version 2.0.4 fixed an issue with internet connection errors and improves the overall speed by 20 30 for Textify . With version 2.0 we re thrilled to introduce Textify : Supercharged Transcription: Transform 5 minutes of speech into text in less than 20 seconds! That s up to 500 faster letting you focus more on creativity and less on waiting. Smart Text Summarization: Our AI driven tech can summarize up to 30 minutes of spoken content. Perfect for those super long voice messages! Accent Friendly: Whether you re from Texas Scotland or Switzerland our improved algorithm is tolerant towards accents and dialects. Multi Lingual Support: Automatically detects and transcribes content in over 50 languages. Your global conversations just got easier! Don t miss out on revolutionizing your transcription experience. Update to Textify 2.0 now!
